            "sent.src.en.a1.l01.009"
          ],
          "learner_language": "zh_tw",
          "title": "主詞代名詞（I / you / he / she / it / we / they）",
          "description": "主詞代名詞用來代替人或事物，放在動詞前面當主詞。",
          "explanation_md": "主詞代名詞用來代替人或事物：\n\n| 代名詞 | 指代對象 | 例句 |\n|--------|---------|------|\n| I | 說話者自己 | **I** am a student. |\n| you | 對方 | **You** are kind. |\n| he | 男性第三人稱 | **He** is happy. |\n| she | 女性第三人稱 | **She** is my teacher. |\n| it | 事物/動物 | **It** is a good day. |\n| we | 包含說話者的複數 | **We** are friends. |\n| they | 第三人稱複數 | **They** are new. |\n\n**注意：**\n- I 在任何位置都要大寫\n- you 可以指「你」或「你們」\n- it 用來指動物或事物"
        },
        "kg.grammar.en.greetings.basic_greetings.v1": {
          "id": "kg.grammar.en.greetings.basic_greetings.v1",
          "kind": "grammar",
          "subcategory": "greetings",
          "level": "A1",
          "surface": "hi / hello / goodbye / good morning / thank you / please",
          "tags": [
            "beginner",
            "greetings",
            "social"
          ],
          "example_sentence_refs": [
            "sent.src.en.a1.l01.004",
            "sent.src.en.a1.l01.011",
            "sent.src.en.a1.l01.012"
          ],
          "learner_language": "zh_tw",
          "title": "基本問候語（hi / hello / goodbye / good morning）",
          "description": "日常生活中最基本的打招呼和禮貌用語。",
          "explanation_md": "基本問候語：\n\n| 英文 | 中文 | 使用時機 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| Hi! | 嗨！ | 非正式打招呼 |\n| Hello! | 你好！ | 通用打招呼 |\n| Good morning! | 早安！ | 早上見面時 |\n| Good afternoon! | 午安！ | 下午見面時 |\n| Good evening! | 晚安！ | 晚上見面時 |\n| Goodbye! | 再見！ | 道別時 |\n| See you! | 回頭見！ | 非正式道別 |\n| Thank you! | 謝謝！ | 表達感謝 |\n| Please | 請 | 禮貌請求 |\n| Sorry | 對不起 | 道歉 |\n| Excuse me | 打擾一下 | 引起注意 |\n\n**回應：**\n- How are you? → I'm fine, thank you. And you?\n- Nice to meet you. → Nice to meet you too.\n- Thank you. → You're welcome."
        },
        "kg.grammar.en.possessive.your_my.v1": {
          "id": "kg.grammar.en.possessive.your_my.v1",
          "kind": "grammar",
          "subcategory": "possessive",
          "level": "A1",
          "surface": "my / your",
          "tags": [
