          "learner_language": "zh_tw",
          "title": "be + from 表示來自哪裡",
          "description": "用 be 動詞 + from 來表示來自哪個國家或城市。",
          "explanation_md": "用 **be + from** 表示來自哪裡：\n\n| 句型 | 例句 |\n|------|------|\n| I am from ... | I **am from** Taiwan. |\n| You are from ... | You **are from** Japan. |\n| He/She is from ... | She **is from** Thailand. |\n\n**疑問句：**\n- **Where are** you **from**?\n- I **am from** America.\n\n**國家和語言：**\n| 國家 | 語言/人 |\n|------|--------|\n| Japan | Japanese |\n| Thailand | Thai |\n| England | English |\n| America | English |\n| Taiwan | Chinese |\n\n**否定句：**\n- I **am not from** England."
        }
      }
